Say '''Casiguran''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Sorsogon]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 30,995 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 87.13 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 4702.	
															
